The,W,C,Web,Notifications,API,is,a,specification,that,defines,an,API,for,handling,end,user,notifications,Notifications,can,alert,users,of,events,such,as,receiving,an,email,outside,the,context,of,a,web,page,It,can,display,notification,on,the,user,s,desktop,or,any,other,static,display,area,outside,the,web,page,The,API,is,flexible,in,how,it,handles,notification,display,and,presentation,options